1. *Uživam* u šetnji parkom. (I enjoy walking in the park.)
2. *Uživajte* u svojoj hrani. (Enjoy your food.)
3. Često *uživam* u čitanju knjiga. (I often enjoy reading books.)
4. Oni *uživaju* u putovanjima. (They enjoy traveling.)
5. *Uživala* sam u predivnom pogledu sa planine. (I enjoyed the beautiful view from the mountain.)
6. *Uživajmo* u suncu dok traje lepo vreme. (Let's enjoy the sun while the weather is nice.)
7. Moramo *uživati* u životu dok smo mladi. (We must enjoy life while we're young.)
8. Ona *uživa* u jogi i meditaciji. (She enjoys yoga and meditation.)
9. *Uživao* sam u koncertu sinoć. (I enjoyed the concert last night.)
10. Možemo *uživati* u prirodi i bez puno novca. (We can enjoy nature without spending a lot of money.)